lead_paragraph: Dina Ammaccapane shot her second 69 in a row for a one-stroke lead after the second round of the L.P.G.A. Corning Classic in Corning, N.Y. Ammaccapane was at six-under 138. The first-round leader, Erica Blasberg (74); Janice Moodie (68); Wendy Ward (70); and Katie Futcher (69) were one back.
